    "htmlContent": "Collaborate on the go. View, share, and mirror designs with just a few taps. With Figma’s official mobile app, you can:\n\nREVIEW YOUR FILES\n* Access Figma, FigJam, Prototype and Slides files.\n* Quickly search for files by name or browse your recently viewed files.\n* Navigate between pages and flows in any file.\n\nCREATE AND REPLY TO COMMENTS\n* Add comments and mention teammates anywhere in a file.\n* Get notified for new comments and replies.\n* Resolve and respond to comments on the go.\n* View a list of all comment threads in a file.\n\nSHARE FILES WITH YOUR TEAM\n* Invite collaborators and share links to your files.\n\nPLAY YOUR PROTOTYPES\n* Play and replay prototypes in full screen.\n* Adjust prototype scaling.\n* Toggle hotspot hints.\n\nMIRROR DESIGNS IN REAL-TIME\n* Sync selected frames from desktop to your mobile device.\n* Watch real-time edits to your designs on your mobile device.\n* Preview how assets in your design look scaled to a device screen.\n\nEXPLORE SLIDES EFFORTLESSLY\n* View and comment on decks in both landscape and portrait mode.\n\nMANAGE PERMISSIONS ON THE FLY\n* Update file permissions to control who can view or edit your work.\n\nBROWSE AND SWITCH WORKSPACES\n* Navigate between teams, plans, and projects tied to your account.\n\nOn iPad, you can also use FigJam to:\n* Sketch with the Apple Pencil to explore and iterate on ideas more fluidly.\n* Share and riff on early thinking with your team.\n* Annotate designs to share feedback.\n* Jot down ideas whenever inspiration strikes.",
